text: Churayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Churayevsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 984 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 34 km from Mishkino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Churayevo, Mishkinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
